2. **trofinetide (Daybue) 2023** = first FDA Rett syndrome. IGF-1 analog peptide. MECP2 loss-of-function downstream IGF-1 axis 회복. quantum-VQE 의 IGF-1R PPI + peptide scaffold modeling.
3. **viloxazine (Qelbree) 2021** = first non-stim ADHD in 20+ year + 6+세. selective NRI multimodal 5-HT 도. atomoxetine (Strattera 2002) 의 next 19년 만의 신약. quantum-VQE 의 NET pocket leverage.
