5. **balovaptan (RG7314) 2018 Phase 2 fail + AFQ056 (mavoglurant) 2014 Phase 3 fail + arbaclofen 2014 Phase 3 fail + gaboxadol 2020 terminated** = ASD/Fragile X/Angelman 4-drug Phase 2/3 실패. quantum-VQE 의 post-mortem pocket re-modeling 의 의의.
6. **oxytocin intranasal STARS trial Pelphrey 2021 negative + secretin 1990s+ negative** = 자폐 hype-cycle 약물 negative. mixed evidence — clinical 의미 없음.
7. **bumetanide 자폐 Phase 2/3 limited evidence + L-DOPA small evidence** = research-stage 자폐 약물. NKCC1 + dopamine precursor 가 small effect.
8. **MECP2 reactivation gene therapy + UBE3A ASO (Ionis + Roche Phase 1) + Angelman gene therapy** = next-gen Rett + Angelman gene therapy + ASO research. Ionis + Roche partnership Phase 1.
9. **22q11 + DiGeorge** = 면역결핍 + 칼슘 결핍 + 정신질환 cross-allergy_immunodef + endocrine_thyroid_pituitary. multifactorial neurodevelopmental + 면역 + 내분비 cross.
